title: Thresh Supportage! x)

embed.description: Been wanting to do this for a while now and finally have gotten round to it. All the clips in this video took about a day to get. Seeing as this is my first video feel free to leave comments of criticisms etc. so that my next ones can be better.

body: Hey all, I've recently been playing a lot of Thresh in dynamic queue and I decided to make a supportage featuring clips from some of my games. Any feedback is welcome and if you do watch the video I hope you enjoy it ^-^.
